# Rebuilding My Business with Tech

This simple HTML/CSS project was created during **Hackathon 1** in the **PLP Academy** program. It reflects my learning progress and my passion for using technology to strengthen and transform small businesses.

## 🎯 Objective
To build a beginner-level web page using HTML and CSS that aligns with my mission of combining technology with entrepreneurship.

## 💻 What I’m Learning at PLP
- HTML & CSS (Web Development)
- Python Programming
- SQL & MySQL Databases
- Git & GitHub
- Fundamentals of Tech, Business, and Problem-Solving

## 🔧 Tools Used
- HTML
- Vanilla CSS
- GitHub

